Maintainer: Jose Endrinal <francis.endrinal@gmail.com>
Description: fastquant allows you to easily backtest investment strategies with 
  as few as 3 lines of Python or R code. Its goal is to promote data driven 
  investments by making quantitative analysis in finance accessible to everyone.
